cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
1. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new deep generative model for conditional image generation and downstream predictive tasks. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The proposed model is evaluated on CIFAR10, a popular image classification dataset. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach to improve the efficiency of conditioning continuous normalizing flows on signals of interest. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper employs gating networks to learn the error tolerances of its ODE solvers for better speed and performance. 
5. cs.SD (Systems and Control): The paper uses ODE solvers to implement the proposed model and improve its efficiency.
